libesmtp: libesmtp (SMTP library)
libesmtp:
libesmtp: libESMTP is a library to manage posting (or submission of) electronic
libesmtp: mail using SMTP to a preconfigured Mail Transport Agent (MTA) such as
libesmtp: Exim. It may be used as part of a Mail User Agent (MUA) or another
libesmtp: program that must be able to post electronic mail but where mail
libesmtp: functionality is not that program's primary purpose.
